{"tid":450564,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想問一個女仔係ex屋企裸體出cos","createTime":"2017-10-28T10:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T08:12:45.000Z","uid":152209,"like":7,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"06a8c23ecc83f291d06a9e8c9a8b2e6494fab8ad","tid":450564,"uid":152209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:16:31.000Z","msg":"佢地影相之外仲會有機會做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw如果你女朋友每日講愛你 但係你唔係到就搵ex傾計<br />\n呃你話冇搵佢 之後仲去日本同ex慶祝生日 浸溫泉 夾公仔<br />\n<br />\n返黎香港之後仲開始傾返電話 到第二次再同ex去(佢ex日本飛去)台灣上機前成個鐘同你講就飛唔傾 但係其實同ex傾左成個鐘先飛 之後再轉日本住佢ex屋企成個月同人瞓同一張床 每日都有拖手出街 仲錫過 之後返黎香港每日起身打俾對方 夜晚傾成5個幾鐘開埋視像 講過我愛你<br />\n<br />\n到今次佢ex包機票叫佢去日本 佢即刻去同樣都係住佢屋企<br />\n今次仲影埋裸cos 專登將同ex影既合照開簿放埋一齊<br />\n想問睇完以上既野 佢話冇鐘意返ex係朋友呢句真定假？<br />\n如果佢係你女朋友你會點？你會點<br />\n佢之前同你講鐘意你有幾成真？<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/whi1te84\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwhi1te84&h=f66e937e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6w71e9qg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6w71e9qg&h=bb23d052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/aripxvkb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Faripxvkb&h=b6a1b180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vm1t6eh5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvm1t6eh5&h=2a0564e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c1c843b776ccb73ee8de9f4b257b6355cc812dc","tid":450564,"uid":2974,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:25:02.000Z","msg":"兩登呢類post黎講，你都算最垃圾，咁都問"},{"pid":"67e13829d3d93be4b6d194bb7ace1b0027bec128","tid":450564,"uid":64211,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:28:48.000Z","msg":"愛因斯坦講過呢個世界上有兩樣嘢係無限<br />\n一係宇宙<br />\n二係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b3e011eb6b02849798aadb78bbd80552a490e6","tid":450564,"ui